flowchart TD
    A[Customer uploads CSV/Excel<br>of 10-100 companies] --> B[iCustomer enriches data:<br>- Company URL<br>- Industry<br>- Location<br>- LinkedIn URL]
    B --> C{User selects<br>waterfall enrichment?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Additional data added:<br>- # of employees<br>- Company stage<br>- Revenue]
    C -->|No| E
    D --> E

    subgraph "Button Flow"
        E[[FIND LOOKALIKES]] --> F[iCustomer displays<br>total lookalikes found<br>e.g., 4,049 companies]
        F --> G[[ADD INTENT SIGNALS]]
        G --> H[User selects from intent signals:<br>- Recently funded<br>- Growing headcount<br>- New product announcement<br>- New executives hired<br>- Traffic increase]
        H --> I[iCustomer narrows lookalikes<br>based on signals<br>e.g., 1,022 matches]
        I --> J[User selects quantity<br>to purchase<br>e.g., 100 per week]
        J --> K[iCustomer displays selected accounts with:<br>- Company name<br>- Website<br>- LinkedIn URL<br>- # of employees<br>- Location<br>- Signal matched<br>- Explanation of fit]
        K --> L[[FIND PEOPLE]]
        L --> M[User specifies target<br>person criteria:<br>- Title<br>- Role<br>- Level]
        M --> N[iCustomer displays<br>total people found<br>e.g., 5,010 contacts]
        N --> O[User selects quantity<br>for segment list<br>e.g., 100 per week]
        O --> P[iCustomer displays selected contacts with<br>full company and contact information]
    end

    P --> Q{Export options}
    Q -->|Option 1| R[[EXPORT TO<br>SMARTLEADS/INSTANTLY]]
    Q -->|Option 2| S[[EXPORT TO<br>LINKEDIN/INSTAGRAM]]

    classDef button fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#009688,color:white,stroke-width:2px,font-weight:bold,border-radius:10px;
    class E,G,L,R,S button;
